<item>
            <title>[LU-17409] ldev parses MGS lines improperly</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17409</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ldev is incorrectly parsing the line specifying the hosts that can&lt;br/&gt;
run the MGS, when of the form&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    gopher1  gopher2  MGS  gopher1/mgs&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;as it assumes every target specified includes a filesystem name,&lt;br/&gt;
like &apos;lustre3-MDT0000&apos;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As a result, ldev never reports MGS targets and cannot identify the hosts or NIDs of those hosts as it should&lt;/p&gt;</description>
